# Comparison: Normal If-Else vs Shorthand If-Else

### Normal If-Else

```python
age = 18

if age >= 18:
    result = "Adult"
else:
    result = "Minor"

print(result)
```

---

### Shorthand If-Else

```python
age = 18

result = "Adult" if age >= 18 else "Minor"

print(result)
